<p class="wikiPara">
A bug fix version of Hibernate Annotations and Entity Manager is out.
In addition to a <a href="http://opensource.atlassian.com/projects/hibernate/browse/ANN?report=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.project:changelog-panel" target="" class="regularLink">bunch</a> of  bug <a href="http://opensource.atlassian.com/projects/hibernate/browse/EJB?report=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.project:changelog-panel" target="" class="regularLink">fixes</a>, they bring some new features:
</p>

<ul class="wikiUnorderedList">
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> support for natural identifiers</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> support for polymorphic associations to classes from multiple tables aka <q>any</q> mapping</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> get rid of the archive browser library dependency</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> support for session scoped interceptors in the <tt>EntityManager</tt>
</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> transparent integration with the latest Hibernate Search collection event listeners</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> experimental Maven 2 POMs</li>
</ul>

<p class="wikiPara">
Maven POMs have always been contributed by the community so far with inconsistent results. As JBoss partly migrates to Maven 2, we will try to bring a more consistent inhouse support from <a href="http://repository.jboss.org/maven2" target="" class="regularLink">the JBoss repository </a>. This is a work in progress, don't hesitate to bring us feedback.</p>
